data.description:
Luxury Custom Home, 1 Acre Horse property with water share. Stunning one owner who meticulously maintained inside and outside of property. Coveted Bluffdale location overlooking valley. Serene setting on dead end street with no neighbors to South or East. Truly private but yet close to everything. Dream kitchen with no expense spared including built in pebble ice maker, built in coffee/hotchocolate maker, built in steamer/sous vide. Open concept living. 6x 6 windows for spectacular views of valley, 8 foot doors up 6 foot doors down. 9 foot ceilings up and down. Floors are all REAL hardwood, countertops are Quartzite. All appliances new and under factory warranty. Custom cabinetry throughout. Built and finished with a more natural classic style. Master bedroom with private master bath downstairs. Home features windows with tinting and custom electric blinds by Sugar House Awning. Real wood 4.5" wood plantation shutters up and down. Custom stained glass from Beehive Glass. 2 fireplaces, 2 water heaters, 2 furnaces, 2 air conditioners and 2 full laundry rooms. .. water softener.  Sink with hot and cold water in garage. Landscaped for easy maintenance, sprinkling system maintained meticulously. Fenced in pasture perfect perfect size for horses or livestock. Pasture planted with range grass. 220 power available outside and your own private RV dump. All of this situated on a beautiful lot with house sitting off road yet plenty of room in back for future shop and/or pool. Furniture and art available separately  BEEHIVE GLASS CUSTOM ELECTRIC BLINDS LUXURY CUSTOM HOME PRIVATE MASTER BATH CUSTOM CABINETRY MASTER BEDROOM DREAM KITCHEN What the seller loves about this home It is serene, private yet so close to everything. Great schools, great neighbors, great layout. Being able to look out to pasture with horses from mater is divine. Window overlooking outside in kitchen is the best. Hardwood floors are perfection, easy to clean and maintain. They give warmth and beauty you cannot achieve with LVP
Recently updated downstairs kitchen and laundry with custom built in cabinet/full size fridge freezer.
Home inspection and appraisal has been done.
Seller to pay 2% commission to buyers agent
We do not need selling agent at this time.

801 865 1346
data.whatILove:
Everything in this home is beautifully done with eye to detail, down to the custom cast iron door knobs.  Peaceful and serene with views that cant be bought
Upscale neighborhood close to schools, parks and shopping. Easy access to Bangeter hwy
